{"tid":671994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先叫俾安全感另一半？","createTime":"2018-05-20T15:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T18:05:21.000Z","uid":46015,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a5516587d1590c39b5f821917406111461340c4a","tid":671994,"uid":46015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"因為另一半根源於內心深處的不安而需要安全感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家會選擇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遷就對方 對方既要求完全做到令另一半安心<br />\n<br />\n例如 另一半唔想你同一個異性太close 你會去選擇同異性朋友減少來往去換取另一半安心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抑或是 同另一半探討不安既感覺來源而大家去解決<br />\n<br />\n例如 了解到因為佢之前拍拖被帽 所以唔鐘意你既異性朋友 好怕又再被帽 咁你會帶另一半認識呢個異性朋友 同另一半解釋之前既事已經過去 我會陪住你走過呢個階段 希望大家一齊努力"},{"pid":"35c637dfd9c79b58cde4bfa70fc43151481630fb","tid":671994,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"根源於內心深處的不安<br />\n女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c32715d7b7194f148646c249dbac2d08c7885e2","tid":671994,"uid":46015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35c637dfd9c79b58cde4bfa70fc43151481630fb","tid":671994,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"根源於內心深處的不安<br />\n女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"唔單止係女人既 男人都會被帽之後拍拖無信心"},{"pid":"cb6fa727d78fcec5b77903ad7b8ecac9e59a5f85","tid":671994,"uid":130298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"帶安全套"},{"pid":"8978236565951ef5583977401b8064f698c1899e","tid":671994,"uid":135060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"有錢"},{"pid":"d4fbf7de86f3b9689039b48ccdb110e53f96c88f","tid":671994,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"著避彈衣 戴頭盔"},{"